1. START  
2. DECLARE three variables: x, y, z  
3. DISPLAY "Enter three values:"  
4. INPUT x, y, z  
5. IF x is greater than or equal to both y and z THEN  
6.      DISPLAY "The largest value is", x  
7. ELSE IF y is greater than or equal to both x and z THEN  
8.      DISPLAY "The largest value is", y  
9. ELSE  
10.      DISPLAY "The largest value is", z  
11. ENDIF  
12. STOP  
